Calculate area of square using C (side square)
Ans) 

code:- // to calculate area of square 
#include <stdio.h>
int main() {
    int side;
    printf("enter side");
    scanf("%d", &side);
    
    printf("area is : %d", side * side);
    return 0;
}

let me explain:-
 
//            -for a statement
int          -to define a variable 
scanf     -to take input
%d         -defines that side is intiger
&            -shows the location of variable 
